.
.br
Lookup a domain, base16 or base32 string\.
.
.br
The \.p2p TLD is optional\.
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBannounce\-start\fR \fIquery\fR[\fI:\fIport\fR\fR]
.
.br
Start to announce a query\.
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBannounce\-stop\fR \fIquery\fR
